# Cesium ion access token — OPTIONAL.
#
# The app works out of the box with the OpenStreetMap default globe (no
# token needed). A Cesium ion token unlocks the two higher-fidelity globe
# styles (Cesium World Imagery + GEBCO World Bathymetry) selectable from
# the in-app Settings dialog. Free-tier is sufficient:
#   https://cesium.com/ion/signup
#
# You can either paste it here at build time (frontend dev workflow) or
# paste it in the in-app Settings dialog at runtime. The runtime path
# persists to the desktop app data settings store. Browser preview uses
# localStorage because it has no Tauri store.
VITE_CESIUM_TOKEN=
